function login(e) { e.preventDefault(); let request = { email: document.getElementById('exampleInputEmail1').value, password: document.getElementById('exampleInputPassword1').value, } axios.post('http://localhost:8000/login', request) .then(resp => { alert(resp.data.message); }) .catch (err => { console.log(err); }) } export default LoginPage;
